Class RentalUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.business.model.properties.RentalUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConferenceRoom, HotelSuite, Office
    public abstract class RentalUnit
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<RentalUnit>
    Rental unit is an abstract class that represents rentable property in the building. It implementgs comparable to compare against itself. It has a list of leases for itself using a SortedLInkListWithIterator

    Jacob Robinson
